<br>
One more thing if we have enough people /groups to take Trak why hold up the charge for someone that did not plan ahead and log themselves at Seb? I know that sounds harsh but buff timer is ticking while the raiding party is waiting for those that log on late to be ported, CoH'd and buffed. Just doesn't seem fair that the possibility for those that are on time to die due to buffs dropping for those that show up late.<br>
<br>
Some raids late comers won't make that big of a difference but when it is important to have as many resist and hp buffs I say charge when we are ready if we already have the groups to kill the mob. <p>I remain your loyal bard and sister,<br>

<br>
Del<br>
